headline: WITTENSTEIN high integrity systems Have Released New SAFERTOS® Source Code Evaluation Packages for the Texas Instruments IWR68xx and AWR68xx Platforms
summary: WITTENSTEIN high integrity systems (WHIS) have released new SAFERTOS® Source Code Evaluation Packages for the Texas Instruments (TI) IWR68xx and AWR68xx platforms. This 30-day package enables developers to explore the advanced capabilities of SAFERTOS® on TI's powerful radar sensor platforms, ideal for safety-critical applications in automotive in-cabin and industrial sectors.
